    "testimonials_alt_KfMCHU": {
      "type": "testimonials-alt",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial_Qrf8FW": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "name": "Dr. Richard Moore",
            "stars": 5,
            "quote": "<p>We saw a noticeable benefit when adding the Berkeley Life capsules into our procedures. Blood flow and healing are critical to the success of our treatments, and the integration of Nitric Oxide has really helped. We continue to promote Berkeley’s N.O. for all of our body procedures as well as men presenting to our men’s clinic – our patients are loving the results.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/RichardMoore.png"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_xCeaVQ": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "name": "Dr. Jeremy Gray",
            "stars": 5,
            "quote": "<p>We encourage all of our patients using GAINSWave for Erectile Dysfunction to use Berkeley Life Nitric Oxide Supplements with treatment. It seems to be the missing link to finding successful improvements with many of our patients.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_6YUzDt": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "name": "Dr. Joy Kong",
            "stars": 5,
            "quote": "<p>My staff and I are very happy that getting our patients to use nitric oxide supplement has become very easy. I send them info and link, and don’t have to worry about the rest. This helps reduce the burden at the clinic, and I like getting the report when patients make the purchase. Thank you for helping patients and helping us!</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_PfPBYB": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "name": "Shane Clarambeau",
            "stars": 5,
            "quote": "<p>I sell a lot of Nitric Oxide. By personally experiencing the benefits of Nitric Oxide it is easy to enthusiastically recommend the product to improve my patients health and life</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_JhBrrW": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "name": "Dr. Kurt Waples",
            "stars": 5,
            "quote": "<p>Heart health, vascular health and dealing with excessive amounts of inflammation in the body have become a normal in nutritional medicine lately. In many of these cases it is an absolute must to support Nitric Oxide (NO) production as a pivotal part of the exercise, diet, nutritional and emotional plan. Berkeley has a great product that goes beyond the typical Arginine NO support.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_yFFVtB": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "name": "Jim Frost",
            "stars": 5,
            "quote": "<p>Once patients try this product, they keep coming back for it. This is particularly the case for our E.D. patients. When it comes to E.D., the results speak for themselves!</p>"
          }
        }
      },
